hadiths[154]{hadithnumber,text}:
5227,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (mulaazimon ko) merey paas pesh karney sey pehley hudood maaf kar diya karo. merey paas koi had wala muqadma aaya to had laziman lageygi.
5228,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (mulaazimon ko) merey paas pesh karney sey pehley hudood maaf kar diya karo. merey paas koi had wala muqadma aaya to had laziman lageygi.
5229,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tak baat tum mein hai, tum hudood maaf kar saktey ho lekin agar koi had wala muqadma mujh tak pahunch gaya to (merey liye) had lagana wajib aur lazim ho jaeyga."
5230,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tak baat tum mein hai, tum hudood maaf kar saktey ho lekin agar koi had wala muqadma mujh tak pahunch gaya to (merey liye) had lagana wajib aur lazim ho jaeyga."
5231,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik Makhzoomi aurat logon sey gharelu saman istimal key liye liya karti thi, phir baad mein mukar jati thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm diya."
5232,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik Makhzoomi aurat logon sey gharelu saman istimal key liye liya karti thi, phir baad mein mukar jati thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm diya."
5233,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Makhzoomi aurat apni padosanon ki maarfat cheezen udhaar ley liya karti thi, phir baad mein mukar jaya karti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm farmaya."
5234,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Makhzoomi aurat apni padosanon ki maarfat cheezen udhaar ley liya karti thi, phir baad mein mukar jaya karti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us ka haath kaat deney ka hukm farmaya."
5235,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat logon key zewrat mang kar ley jaya karti thi aur phir wapis karney sey inkar kar deti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aurat Allah aur uskey Rasool key samney elaniya-tauba karey aur jo kuchh is ney logon sey liya hai in ko wapis kerey. (lekin wo aurat na maana tu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal ! utho aur iska haath kaat do.
5236,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat logon key zewrat mang kar ley jaya karti thi aur phir wapis karney sey inkar kar deti thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye aurat Allah aur uskey Rasool key samney elaniya-tauba karey aur jo kuchh is ney logon sey liya hai in ko wapis kerey. (lekin wo aurat na maana tu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Bilal ! utho aur iska haath kaat do.
5237,"Hazrat Naafey (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein istimal key liye zewrat mang liya karti thi. is tarah us ney kafi zewrat ikhattey kar liye. phir wo apney paas rakh liye (aur wapis karney sey mukar gaee) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is aurat ko chahiye ke wo tauba karey aur jo kuchh us ney liya hai, wapis kerey. aap ney kaee dafa farmaya magar wo na maani. aakhir us ka haath kaat diya gaya."
5238,"Hazrat Naafey (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein istimal key liye zewrat mang liya karti thi. is tarah us ney kafi zewrat ikhattey kar liye. phir wo apney paas rakh liye (aur wapis karney sey mukar gaee) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is aurat ko chahiye ke wo tauba karey aur jo kuchh us ney liya hai, wapis kerey. aap ney kaee dafa farmaya magar wo na maani. aakhir us ka haath kaat diya gaya."
5239,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Makhzoom ki eik aurat ney chori kar li. usey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. us ney Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key yahan panah hasil kar li. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar (chori karney wali) Fatima binte Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta. phir is aurat ka haath kaat diya gaya.
5240,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke banu Makhzoom ki eik aurat ney chori kar li. usey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. us ney Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) key yahan panah hasil kar li. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar (chori karney wali) Fatima binte Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta. phir is aurat ka haath kaat diya gaya.
5241,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey marwi hai ke banu Makhzoom ki eik aurat ney dusrey logon key wastey sey zewar istimal key liye liya, baad mein mukar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey us ka haath kaat diya gaya."
5242,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey marwi hai ke banu Makhzoom ki eik aurat ney dusrey logon key wastey sey zewar istimal key liye liya, baad mein mukar gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey us ka haath kaat diya gaya."
5243,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey is jaisi riwayat aur sanad bhi aati hai.
5244,Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey is jaisi riwayat aur sanad bhi aati hai.
5245,"Hazrat Sufiyan sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik Makhzoomi aurat logon sey saman mang kar ley jati , phir (wapis karney sey) mukar jaya karti thi. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein pesh kiya gaya, isi ke sath uskey barey mein (maafi ki) sifarish bhi ki gaee. aap ney farmaya : agar (meri beti) Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta. Sufiyan sey puchha gaya : (ye riwayat) kis ney bayan ki hai? unhoney kaha : Ayub bin Musa ney Zohri sey, unhoney Urwa sey, unhoney Aaisha sey. (Insha-Allah)."
5246,"Hazrat Sufiyan sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik Makhzoomi aurat logon sey saman mang kar ley jati , phir (wapis karney sey) mukar jaya karti thi. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki adaalat mein pesh kiya gaya, isi ke sath uskey barey mein (maafi ki) sifarish bhi ki gaee. aap ney farmaya : agar (meri beti) Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta. Sufiyan sey puchha gaya : (ye riwayat) kis ney bayan ki hai? unhoney kaha : Ayub bin Musa ney Zohri sey, unhoney Urwa sey, unhoney Aaisha sey. (Insha-Allah)."
5247,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney chori kar li. usey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. logon (aurat key rishtey-daaron) ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney sifarish ki kon himmat kar sakta hai? Usama shayad kerey. unhoney Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha. Usama ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (us aurat ki maafi ki) sifarish kar di. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Usama ! banu Israel isi liye halak huye they ke jab un mein koi buland martaba shakhs koi had phalang leta to usey chhod detey aur had na lagatey. aur jab koi kam-martaba shakhs ghalati kar beth'ta to is par had qaaim kar detey. agar uski bajaey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5248,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney chori kar li. usey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. logon (aurat key rishtey-daaron) ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key samney sifarish ki kon himmat kar sakta hai? Usama shayad kerey. unhoney Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha. Usama ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey (us aurat ki maafi ki) sifarish kar di. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Usama ! banu Israel isi liye halak huye they ke jab un mein koi buland martaba shakhs koi had phalang leta to usey chhod detey aur had na lagatey. aur jab koi kam-martaba shakhs ghalati kar beth'ta to is par had qaaim kar detey. agar uski bajaey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5249,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaat diya. log kehney lagey : hamein ye khayal na tha ke aap us ko is had tak saza dengey. aap ney farmaya : agar (is key bajaey) Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5250,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik chor laya gaya. aap ney us ka haath kaat diya. log kehney lagey : hamein ye khayal na tha ke aap us ko is had tak saza dengey. aap ney farmaya : agar (is key bajaey) Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5251,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure mubarak mein chori kar li. log kehney lagey : hum to iskey barey mein aap sey baat nahin kar saktey aur bhi koi nahin kar sakta magar Usama jo aap ko bahut piyarey hain. Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap sey sifarish ki to aap ney farmaya : aey Usama ! Bani-Israel is jaisey kamon ki wajeh sey halak huye. jab un mein sey koi buland martaba shakhs chori kar leta to us ko chhod detey aur agar koi kam martaba shakhs un mein chori kar bethta to us ka haath kaat detey. agar (chori karney wali) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5252,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure mubarak mein chori kar li. log kehney lagey : hum to iskey barey mein aap sey baat nahin kar saktey aur bhi koi nahin kar sakta magar Usama jo aap ko bahut piyarey hain. Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap sey sifarish ki to aap ney farmaya : aey Usama ! Bani-Israel is jaisey kamon ki wajeh sey halak huye. jab un mein sey koi buland martaba shakhs chori kar leta to us ko chhod detey aur agar koi kam martaba shakhs un mein chori kar bethta to us ka haath kaat detey. agar (chori karney wali) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima hoti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5253,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : eik aurat ney dusrey logon ki maarfat kuch zewrat aarzi taur par istimal key liye liye. wo log to maroof they magar wo aurat maroof nahin thi. us ney wo zewrat bech diye aur qeemat hazam kar li. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to uskey ghar waley (sifarish key liye) Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhagey. Hazrat Usama Raziallahu anhu ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey uski sifarish kar di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra (ghussey sey) surkh ho gaya. phir aap ney farmaya : to merey paas Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda hudood mein sey eik had na laganey ki sifarish kar raha hai? Usama ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye bakhshish ki dua farmaiye. phir usi din Zohar key baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (khitab key liye) uthey. Allah Taala ki tareef farmaai jo uski shaan key laaiq hai. phir farmaya : sun lo ! tum sey pehley log us bina par halak huye ke jab un mein sey koi buland martaba shakhs chori kar leta tha to usey chhod detey aur jab koi kamzor shakhs chori kar leta to usey had laga detey. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima chori karti to main us ka haath bhi kaat deta. phir aap ney us aurat ka haath kaat diya.
5254,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : eik aurat ney dusrey logon ki maarfat kuch zewrat aarzi taur par istimal key liye liye. wo log to maroof they magar wo aurat maroof nahin thi. us ney wo zewrat bech diye aur qeemat hazam kar li. usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to uskey ghar waley (sifarish key liye) Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhagey. Hazrat Usama Raziallahu anhu ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey uski sifarish kar di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra (ghussey sey) surkh ho gaya. phir aap ney farmaya : to merey paas Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda hudood mein sey eik had na laganey ki sifarish kar raha hai? Usama ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye bakhshish ki dua farmaiye. phir usi din Zohar key baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (khitab key liye) uthey. Allah Taala ki tareef farmaai jo uski shaan key laaiq hai. phir farmaya : sun lo ! tum sey pehley log us bina par halak huye ke jab un mein sey koi buland martaba shakhs chori kar leta tha to usey chhod detey aur jab koi kamzor shakhs chori kar leta to usey had laga detey. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad ki jaan hai ! agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima chori karti to main us ka haath bhi kaat deta. phir aap ney us aurat ka haath kaat diya.
5255,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik Makhzoomi aurat jisney chori ki thi, ki wajeh sey Quraish badey fikrmand huye. wo kehney lagey : iski sifarish Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kon kerega? phir (khud hi) kehney lagey : iski himmat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mehbub Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma key siwa kon kar sakta hai ! Hazrat Usama ney aap sey uski sifarish ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda hudood mein sey eik had (ko nafiz na kerney) ki baabat sifarish kar raha hai? phir aap khadey huye aur khitab kartey huye farmaya : tum logon sey pehley log isi bina par halak huye ke jab un mein sey koi buland martaba shakhs chori kar leta to usey chhod detey they aur jab koi kamzor shakhs chori kar leta to us ko had laga detey. Allah ki qism ! agar (farz kijiye) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima bhi chori karti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta."
5256,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke eik Makhzoomi aurat jisney chori ki thi, ki wajeh sey Quraish badey fikrmand huye. wo kehney lagey : iski sifarish Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kon kerega? phir (khud hi) kehney lagey : iski himmat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mehbub Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma key siwa kon kar sakta hai ! Hazrat Usama ney aap sey uski sifarish ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda hudood mein sey eik had (ko nafiz na kerney) ki baabat sifarish kar raha hai? phir aap khadey huye aur khitab kartey huye farmaya : tum logon sey pehley log isi bina par halak huye ke jab un mein sey koi buland martaba shakhs chori kar leta to usey chhod detey they aur jab koi kamzor shakhs chori kar leta to us ko had laga detey. Allah ki qism ! agar (farz kijiye) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima bhi chori karti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta."
5257,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Quraish key eik qabiley banu Makhzoom ki eik aurat ney chori kar li. usey pakad kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. uskey rishtey-daar kehney lagey ke kon iski sifarish kar sakta hai? kuchh log kehney lagey : Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ye kaam kar saktey hain. Usama aap key paas aaye aur us aurat ki sifarish ki. aap ney unhen daantaa aur farmaya : Bani-Israel ka haal ye tha ke jab unka koi buland martaba shakhs chori karta tha to usey chhod detey. (kuchh nahin kehtey they.) aur jab koi kam martaba shakhs chori kar leta tha to us ka haath kaat detey. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar (meri beti) Fatima binte Muhammad chori karti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5258,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai unhoney farmaya : Quraish key eik qabiley banu Makhzoom ki eik aurat ney chori kar li. usey pakad kar Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. uskey rishtey-daar kehney lagey ke kon iski sifarish kar sakta hai? kuchh log kehney lagey : Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ye kaam kar saktey hain. Usama aap key paas aaye aur us aurat ki sifarish ki. aap ney unhen daantaa aur farmaya : Bani-Israel ka haal ye tha ke jab unka koi buland martaba shakhs chori karta tha to usey chhod detey. (kuchh nahin kehtey they.) aur jab koi kam martaba shakhs chori kar leta tha to us ka haath kaat detey. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar (meri beti) Fatima binte Muhammad chori karti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta.
5259,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Quraish ko eik Makhzoomi aurat key mamley ney pareshan kar diya jisney chori kar li thi. wo kehney lagey : iskey barey mein kon sifarish kerega? phir khud hi kehney lagey : iski himmat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mehbub Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma key siwa kon kar sakta hai ! Hazrat Usama ney aap sey sifarish ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum sey pehley log isi bina par halak huye ke jab un mein koi bada (choudhri) chori kar leta to usey chhod detey they aur jab koi kam martaba shakhs chori kar leta tha to is par had laga detey they. Allah ki qism ! agar Muhammad ki beti Fatima chori karti to main us ka haath bhi kaat deta.
5260,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Quraish ko eik Makhzoomi aurat key mamley ney pareshan kar diya jisney chori kar li thi. wo kehney lagey : iskey barey mein kon sifarish kerega? phir khud hi kehney lagey : iski himmat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mehbub Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma key siwa kon kar sakta hai ! Hazrat Usama ney aap sey sifarish ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum sey pehley log isi bina par halak huye ke jab un mein koi bada (choudhri) chori kar leta to usey chhod detey they aur jab koi kam martaba shakhs chori kar leta tha to is par had laga detey they. Allah ki qism ! agar Muhammad ki beti Fatima chori karti to main us ka haath bhi kaat deta.
5261,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehade-mubarak mein ghazwa fateh-Makka key moqe par eik aurat ney chori kar li to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. Hazrat Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma ney uskey barey mein aap sey baat ki. (maafi ki sifarish ki.) jab unhoney aap sey baat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra anwar mutghaiyar (ghussey sey surkh) ho gaya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda hudood mein sey eik had (ko saaqit kerney) ki baabat sifarish kar raha hai? Hazrat Usama ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye maafi ki dua farmaiye. phir jab Zohar (ki namaz) hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur Allah ki tareef ki jo Allah ki shaan jaleela key mutabiq thi. phir farmaya : sun lo ! tum sey pehley log isi bina par halak huye ke jab un mein koi ooncha (bada) aadmi chori kar leta to usey chhod detey they. (kuchh na kehtey they) aur jab koi kamzor aadmi chori kar bethta tha to is par had laagu kar detey (usey saza detey) they. phir farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar Fatima binte Muhammad bhi chori karti to main us ka haath bhi kaat deta.
5262,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehade-mubarak mein ghazwa fateh-Makka key moqe par eik aurat ney chori kar li to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. Hazrat Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma ney uskey barey mein aap sey baat ki. (maafi ki sifarish ki.) jab unhoney aap sey baat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra anwar mutghaiyar (ghussey sey surkh) ho gaya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya to Allah Taala ki muqarrar karda hudood mein sey eik had (ko saaqit kerney) ki baabat sifarish kar raha hai? Hazrat Usama ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye maafi ki dua farmaiye. phir jab Zohar (ki namaz) hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur Allah ki tareef ki jo Allah ki shaan jaleela key mutabiq thi. phir farmaya : sun lo ! tum sey pehley log isi bina par halak huye ke jab un mein koi ooncha (bada) aadmi chori kar leta to usey chhod detey they. (kuchh na kehtey they) aur jab koi kamzor aadmi chori kar bethta tha to is par had laagu kar detey (usey saza detey) they. phir farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar Fatima binte Muhammad bhi chori karti to main us ka haath bhi kaat deta.
5263,Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey mursalan riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ehade-mubarak mein fateh Makka ki jang key waqt eik aurat ney chori kar li. uski qom key log ghabra kar Hazrat Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma key paas aaye ke wo uski sifarish farma den. jab Hazrat Usama ney aap sey uski baabat baat cheet ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key chehre aqdas ka rang badal gaya. aap ney farmaya : kya to Allah Taala ki hudood mein sey eik had key barey mein sifarish karta hai? Usama ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey liye istighfar farmaeyn. Zohar key baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khutbey key liye khadey huye aur Allah Taala ki tareef farmaaee jo uski shaan key laaiq hai. phir farmaya : Amma-baad (aey logo ! ) tum sey pehley log is bina par tabah huye ke jab un mein koi taqatwer shakhs chori karta to us ko chhod detey. aur jab koi kamzor shakhs chori karta to is par had nafiz kar detey. qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar (farz karo) Fatima binte Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) chori karti to main us ka bhi haath kaat deta. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us aurat ka haath kaatney ka hukm diya. us ka haath kaat diya gaya. lekin iskey baad us ney bahut achchhi tauba kar li. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : uskey baad wo merey paas aaya karti thi aur main uski guzaarishey aur zarooriyaat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya karti thi.
