5351,Hazrat Ata aur Mujahid sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aiman bin Ummey Aiman ney marfooan (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman) bayan farmaya ke chor ka haath dhaal ki qeemat sey kam mein nahin kaataa jaeyga. aur dhaal ki qeemat un dino eik deenar thi.
