5358,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke dhaal ki qeemat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein das dirham lagai jati thi.
5359,ye riwayat Hazrat Ata sey mursal bhi aati hai. (sahabi key zikr key baghair.)
5360,ye riwayat Hazrat Ata sey mursal bhi aati hai. (sahabi key zikr key baghair.)
5361,"Hazrat Ata ney farmaya : kam se kam miqdaar jiski chori mein haath kaataa jata hai, dhaal ki qeemat hai. aur dhaal ki qeemat un dino das dirham thi. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : wo Hazrat Aiman jin ki hadees hum is sey pehley (is baab mein) zikr kar chukey hain merey khayal key mutabiq wo sahabi nahin. un sey eik aur hadees marwi hai jo hamari baat ki daleel hai. (aur wo hadees ye hai, yani 4957)."
5362,"Hazrat Ata ney farmaya : kam se kam miqdaar jiski chori mein haath kaataa jata hai, dhaal ki qeemat hai. aur dhaal ki qeemat un dino das dirham thi. Abu Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : wo Hazrat Aiman jin ki hadees hum is sey pehley (is baab mein) zikr kar chukey hain merey khayal key mutabiq wo sahabi nahin. un sey eik aur hadees marwi hai jo hamari baat ki daleel hai. (aur wo hadees ye hai, yani 4957)."
5363,"Hazrat Ata ney Hazrat Aiman Mola ibne Zuber ya Mola Zuber sey bayan kiya, wo riwayat kartey hain Hazrat Tabia sey aur wo bayan kartey hain Hazrat Kaab sey, unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah wuzu kerey. phir Isha ki namaz (ba-jamaat) padhey, phir iskey baad chaar rakaten padhey un mein rukoo sajda pura pura karey aur jo kuchh padhey, soch samajh kar padhey to ye chaar rakaat uskey liye (sawab key lihaz sey) lailatul-qadr ki tarah ban jaeyngi."
5364,"Hazrat Ata ney Hazrat Aiman Mola ibne Zuber ya Mola Zuber sey bayan kiya, wo riwayat kartey hain Hazrat Tabia sey aur wo bayan kartey hain Hazrat Kaab sey, unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah wuzu kerey. phir Isha ki namaz (ba-jamaat) padhey, phir iskey baad chaar rakaten padhey un mein rukoo sajda pura pura karey aur jo kuchh padhey, soch samajh kar padhey to ye chaar rakaat uskey liye (sawab key lihaz sey) lailatul-qadr ki tarah ban jaeyngi."
5365,"Hazrat Aiman Mola ibne-Umar Hazrat Tabia sey aur wo Hazrat Kaab sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah wuzu kerey. phir Isha ki namaz ba-jamaat padhey phir baad mein us jaisi chaar rakaten aur padhey, un mein (tawajjoh key sath) qirat karey aur rukoo sajdey mukammal kerey. usey Lailatul-qadr ki ibadat key barabar sawab milega."
5366,"Hazrat Aiman Mola ibne-Umar Hazrat Tabia sey aur wo Hazrat Kaab sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs wuzu karey aur achchhi tarah wuzu kerey. phir Isha ki namaz ba-jamaat padhey phir baad mein us jaisi chaar rakaten aur padhey, un mein (tawajjoh key sath) qirat karey aur rukoo sajdey mukammal kerey. usey Lailatul-qadr ki ibadat key barabar sawab milega."
5367,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke dhaal ki qeemat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein das dirham thi.
5368,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke dhaal ki qeemat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daure-mubarak mein das dirham thi.
5369,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya ke haath kitney (maal) main kaataa jaeyga? aap ney farmaya : darkht par lagey huye phal todney sey haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, albatta jab phal tod kar dher laga diya gaya ho to dhaal ki qeemat key barabar chori karney sey haath kaataa jaeyga. (isi tarah) pahad par charti bakri charaney sey haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, albatta bakri baadey mein aa jaey to phir usey charaney mein haath kaataa jaeyga ba-sharte ke uski qeemat dhaal sey kam na ho."
5370,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib key pardada (Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha gaya ke haath kitney (maal) main kaataa jaeyga? aap ney farmaya : darkht par lagey huye phal todney sey haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, albatta jab phal tod kar dher laga diya gaya ho to dhaal ki qeemat key barabar chori karney sey haath kaataa jaeyga. (isi tarah) pahad par charti bakri charaney sey haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, albatta bakri baadey mein aa jaey to phir usey charaney mein haath kaataa jaeyga ba-sharte ke uski qeemat dhaal sey kam na ho."
5371,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey darkht par lagey huye phal ko todney key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : agar to koi hajat mand phal tod kar kha ley, sath na ley jaey to usey kuchh nahin kaha jaeyga. aur agar wo phal sath bhi ley jaey to us sey dugni qeemat wasul ki jaeygi aur saza bhi di jaeygi. aur agar khaliyiaan mein rakhney key baad kisi shakhs ney koi phal utha liya aur uski qeemat dhaal ki qeemat key barabar ya zayed ho to us ka haath kaat diya jaeyga. aur agar dhaal ki qeemat sey kam churaayaa to us sey dugni qeemat ley li jaeygi aur usey saza bhi milegi."
5372,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey darkht par lagey huye phal ko todney key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : agar to koi hajat mand phal tod kar kha ley, sath na ley jaey to usey kuchh nahin kaha jaeyga. aur agar wo phal sath bhi ley jaey to us sey dugni qeemat wasul ki jaeygi aur saza bhi di jaeygi. aur agar khaliyiaan mein rakhney key baad kisi shakhs ney koi phal utha liya aur uski qeemat dhaal ki qeemat key barabar ya zayed ho to us ka haath kaat diya jaeyga. aur agar dhaal ki qeemat sey kam churaayaa to us sey dugni qeemat ley li jaeygi aur usey saza bhi milegi."
5373,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Muzena qabiley ka eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! pahad par charney wali bakri (ya kisi aur janwer) key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : dugni qeemat aur jismani saza. janwer ki chori mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, siwaye iske ke wo janwer baadey mein ho aur uski qeemat dhaal key barabar ya us sey zayed ho to phir uski chori par haath kaat diya jaaeyga aur agar uski qeemat us sey kam ho to dugni qeemat li jaeygi aur bator saza kodey lagaey jaeyngey. us aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! darkht par lagey huye phal key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : is mein bhi dugni qeemat aur jismani saza. darkht par lagey huye phal ki chori mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. albatta agar phal khaliyiaan mein laga diya jaey, uskey baad chori ho aur uski qeemat dhaal key barabar ya zayed ho to haath kaataa jaeyga. agar phal dhaal ki qeemat sey kam ho to chor sey dugni qeemat li jaeygi aur jismani saza key taur par kodey bhi lagaey jaeyngey."
5374,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Muzena qabiley ka eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! pahad par charney wali bakri (ya kisi aur janwer) key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : dugni qeemat aur jismani saza. janwer ki chori mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga, siwaye iske ke wo janwer baadey mein ho aur uski qeemat dhaal key barabar ya us sey zayed ho to phir uski chori par haath kaat diya jaaeyga aur agar uski qeemat us sey kam ho to dugni qeemat li jaeygi aur bator saza kodey lagaey jaeyngey. us aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! darkht par lagey huye phal key barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? aap ney farmaya : is mein bhi dugni qeemat aur jismani saza. darkht par lagey huye phal ki chori mein haath nahin kaataa jaeyga. albatta agar phal khaliyiaan mein laga diya jaey, uskey baad chori ho aur uski qeemat dhaal key barabar ya zayed ho to haath kaataa jaeyga. agar phal dhaal ki qeemat sey kam ho to chor sey dugni qeemat li jaeygi aur jismani saza key taur par kodey bhi lagaey jaeyngey."
5375,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur giri (khajoor key maghz) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5376,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur giri (khajoor key maghz) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5377,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (goodey) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5378,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (goodey) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5379,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
5380,"Hazrat Raafey bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : phal aur gaabhey (ki chori) main haath nahin kaataa jaeyga."
